Author: _fidgetspinner
Text: it's our disordered minds. i feel like all mirrors are lying to me because i know that i weigh more than i used to, but i'm starting to not look as big as i thought when i look in the mirror....? it's so weird. but then in all photos i look huge so the photos must be right... right?! ugh help my brain is fucked

Author: katarina-stratford
Text: I spent 15 minutes this morning just standing still and staring at the mirror, trying to work out where the fuck it all went *cause the numbers changed but I look the same wtf*
